  <brief_title>Multi-national, Safety and Performance Study of New Ostomy Product Compared to Standard Care</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-labelled, Randomised, Controlled, Comparative, Multi-national, Cross-over Study Investigating the Safety and Performance of a New 2-piece Ostomy Product Compared to 2-piece Standard Care Ostomy Products</official_title>
  <sponsors>
